# Copy this file to ".env" and fill in the value(s) below.
#
# Formspree form ID — the contact form posts submissions here, which Formspree
# forwards to your inbox. Create a free form at https://formspree.io, then copy
# the ID from the form's endpoint URL (https://formspree.io/f/XXXXXXXX -> XXXXXXXX).
#
# For local dev: put it in a ".env" file (gitignored).
# For production (AWS Amplify): add it as a build environment variable in the
# Amplify console (App settings -> Environment variables) with the same name.
#
# If this is left unset, the contact form falls back to opening the visitor's
# email client (mailto) instead.
VITE_FORMSPREE_ID=
